<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
24节气是科学还是文化？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=7d03a8b89abc05beecd7a8cf&lemmaId=453238&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">

好消息！二十四节气正式列入人类非物质文化遗产名录了！新华社报: 昨天，联合国教科文组织保护非物质文化遗产政府间委员会召开第11届常会，中国的“二十四节气”被正式列入联合国教科文组织人类非物质文化遗产代表作名录。...</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-06-15</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">120</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="12a05361043f93d312341260">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=d852f025&authorId=75b0538749bbaa1c06ce6121&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/d1a20cf431adcbef120248c3a0af2edda2cc9fc4.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>海叔说春秋</strong>
<span>独立历史研究者，专注于春秋战国。</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=12a05361043f93d312341260&lemmaId=453238&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/d52a2834349b033bf77b558a18ce36d3d439bdeb.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
诸侯列国都是24节气，为什么齐国偏偏要有30个节气？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=12a05361043f93d312341260&lemmaId=453238&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
在春秋战国时代，中原人终归还是以农业为主的地区，农业生产与天文历法的关系非常密切。春耕秋收要看天，祭祀祖先也要看天，朝堂中有专门的掌管天文历法的官员，谓之于“太卜”、“春官”或是“宗伯”。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-11-15</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">39</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="427d0d5adb9ad7c9075bcc95">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=f492dda4&authorId=6797281051b8b21d5963cb21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/810a19d8bc3eb1357ef6d779aa1ea8d3fd1f443a.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>蝌蚪五线谱</strong>
<span>北京市科协主办科普网站</span>
